							connections with the community.</b
						>
					</p>
				</div>
				<div class="image">
					<img src={"https://picsum.photos/500"} />
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="team-member">
				<div class="image">
					<img src={"https://picsum.photos/500"} />
				</div>
				<div class="text">
					<div class="topline">
						<h2>Avion Goordeen</h2>
						<p>Task Force Director</p>
					</div>
					<div class="description">
						<p>{faker.lorem.paragraphs(1)}</p>
						<p>{faker.lorem.paragraphs(1)}</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="get-involved">
				<h2>Get involved with our work!</h2>
