		</div>
	</section>
	<section class="task-force" id="policy">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="info">
				<div class="text">
					<h1>Policy Task Force</h1>
					<p>
						PRISM’s Policy Task Force works to advance innovative laws and
						policies and pushes back against bad bills to ensure that no one
						suffers discrimination or harassment on the basis of their sexual
						orientation, race, or gender identity.
					</p>
					<p>
						The Policy Task Force solves challenges at the local, state, and
						national levels, with an emphasis on fighting for the LGBTQ+
						community, <b
							>especially LGBTQ+ people of color across South Florida.</b
						>
					</p>
				</div>
				<div class="image">
					<img src={"https://picsum.photos/500"} />
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="team-member">
